high_descs: Go to toilet, turn right.  Proceed to counter.
Pick up candle at back of counter, close to the wall.
Turn left, proceed to sink on your right.  Turn right to face sink.
Open second drawer down, closest to wall.  Put candle in drawer in the left lower corner.  Shut drawer.
Turn around, proceed to garbage can on right.  Turn right to face garbage can.
Pick up toilet paper out of garbage can.
Turn right, go to drawers.  Open bottom left side drawer.
Put toilet paper in drawer, directly above candle, close drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put candle and toilet paper in left side of a drawer.
